Class Room

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.java.questfortheabodeth.environments.Room
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.jsfml.graphics.Drawable

    public class Room
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.jsfml.graphics.Drawable
    Class that models a room object in the game. Every room contains all the environment objects to draw and any enemies that are to be spawned in the room
